						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Stone fixed into the raised platform in the Hanumān temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 1676.</p>						

						<p>This record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1597, Rākshasa, Pushya, ba. 15,</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D., 1676 January 5, Wednesday.</hi></p>						

						<p>The inscription records that Dēśāyi Liṅgapagauḍa of <hi rend="bold">Gutaḷa</hi> made grants (of land) in Maḍatira-sīme which was his <hi rend="italic">uṁbaḷi</hi> to several individuals mentioned.</p>						

						</summary>
